(b) "Digital asset" does not include any of the following:
(i) A security.
(ii) Game-related digital content.
(iii) A gift card.
(iv) A loyalty card.
(19) "Digital asset account" means a customer account, a digital asset wallet,
or other repository device maintained by an owner with a digital asset holder that
may contain one or more types of digital assets, money, or other property.
(20) "Digital asset holder" means a holder that establishes or maintains a
digital asset account for an owner.
(21) "Digital asset wallet" means a software application or other mechanism
that provides a means to hold, store, or transfer a digital asset.
(22) "Private key" means a unique element of cryptographic data used to sign
and authorize a transfer of a digital asset.
